caller_intent: The caller wants to add their daughter to their existing insurance policy, despite the daughter not yet owning a car in North Carolina and the car purchase being delayed for two weeks.
resolution_steps: Agent asked for the caller's name and policy details to look up their account.
Agent noted the policy number was only for support and needed to transfer the caller to the correct agent.
Agent paused to clarify the situation but did not resolve the request before the call ended.
knowledge_required: Verifying driver eligibility before policy changes
systems_referenced: Alliance Insurance Services account management system
summary: Caller sought to add their daughter to their policy despite the daughter not yet owning a car in NC. Agent initiated account lookup but did not resolve the request before transferring the call. The situation requires verifying coverage eligibility for a driver without a vehicle.
